XCNV package licensing scope

The independently authored R package implementation under R/, tests/, man/,
inst/ (except notices about external resources), DESCRIPTION, NAMESPACE,
README.Rmd, README.md, NEWS.md, and the package maintenance scripts is licensed
under the GNU General Public License version 2 or, at your option, any later
version (GPL >= 2).

This grant does not apply to the historical upstream XCNV files under data/ or
example_data/, including the trained model.
The pinned upstream XCNV repository contains no license grant. Those historical
files are excluded from the built R package and remain release-gated pending
permission from their copyright holders.

This grant also does not apply to Genotek ClassifyCNV commit
148757c4d6cbfb8d60878535686f40219b63a7a8. Its LICENSE.md permits
academic/research use only and explicitly prohibits modification and
redistribution without author permission. No ClassifyCNV source code or bundled
database is included in this package. A GPL-compatible port requires a separate
written permission or relicensing grant from the ClassifyCNV copyright holders.

External scientific resources retain their own terms. See
inst/RESOURCE-LICENSES.md.
